entries.femaleVariant: What's going on?
How's Jake holdin' up?
Not so great. We've managed to stem the bleeding, but... without that implant...
What's goin' on?
Jake got hit. Badly. He needs a new kidney as of this minute.
Only problem is, he's got sickle cell anemia. He'll need a specially customized kidney implant.
I'm sure you can find one in the city.
Right. Dakota called up her contact at one of the hospitals. Was told they could work something out...
Did Raffen Shiv shoot him?
Mhm. We pulled through this time... barely.
You can find an implant like that in Night City. No questions asked...
entries.maleVariant: You can find an implant like that in Night City, no questions asked...

entries.femaleVariant: Raffen Shiv – were they the ones behind this?
But...?
You can count on me.
I'm sorry, but I can't.
You can count on me.
Dakota's contact works at a hospital in Little China. All you have to do is pick up the implant – the money will take a more secure route.
I'm sorry, but... I can't. At least, not right now.
I understand. In case you change your mind, there's still a bit of time left.
I'll help Jake.
But that means getting to the city, and you see the state the camp's in... Raffen Shiv could come back at any moment. It's all hands on deck.
We'll handle it. Don't ask me how, but we will. I give you my word.
As you can imagine, that kinda thing isn't easy to come by out here in the Badlands.
Shrapnel caught Jake... half an inch below his flak jacket.
That's a tough break.
It still isn't too late to save him... but time's runnin' out.
You know where this is going, V. I won't beat around the bush... Can you help us?
I know, V.
Gotcha. See ya later, then.
I've thought things through.
